Author contributions
J.L.A., J.A.A., E.B. and E.M.S. designed and performed the experiments. Experiments were done at Quillen College of Medicine, East Tennessee State University, Johnson City, TN. V.J. and A.V. developed the signal processing methodology. S.S. implemented the signal processing tools. J.L.A., S.S. and E.B. analysed the data. All authors contributed to writing the paper and approved the ﬁnal version of the manuscript.
